Package de.altwagen.Exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CarCountBelowZeroException
    This Exception will be thrown, when you try to remove a car from a locations where the car count is already 0
    DeleteLocationWithCarsException
    This Exception will be thrown, when you try to delete a location, which has cars stored (carCount not 0)
